539
00:53:29,636 --> 00:53:36,980
[SPEAKER_03]: So the situation I'm thinking of is like my task would need to be done in conjunction with another person.

540
00:53:38,721 --> 00:53:46,625
[SPEAKER_03]: And so would we need to, is there a way to have an open meeting outside of our normal open meeting?

541
00:53:46,645 --> 00:53:50,187
[SPEAKER_03]: Like could we call an open meeting to work on something together?

542
00:53:50,958 --> 00:54:07,223
[SPEAKER_03]: let's say I'm working on an email communication that's going out to the general public, but I need information from Tom, like we need to look at it together.

543
