545
00:54:18,078 --> 00:54:19,739
[SPEAKER_03]: Is that what we would do?

546
00:54:19,759 --> 00:54:21,401
[SPEAKER_02]: That would be absolutely fine.

547
00:54:21,521 --> 00:54:21,721
[SPEAKER_02]: Yep.

548
00:54:22,262 --> 00:54:25,645
[SPEAKER_02]: And so it doesn't, that would be a working group essentially, right?

549
00:54:25,705 --> 00:54:33,431
