554
00:54:57,066 --> 00:54:58,706
[SPEAKER_02]: That would not be an issue at all, Linda.

555
00:54:58,826 --> 00:54:59,406
[SPEAKER_02]: Good question.

556
00:54:59,926 --> 00:55:00,166
[SPEAKER_02]: Cool.

